\id HAB Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h HABAKKUK 
\toc1 HABAKKUK 
\toc2 Habakkuk 
\toc3 Hab 
\mt1 HABAKKUK  
\mt2 (The Book of Habakkuk)  
\is1 Habakkuk Cabu Kawng  
\im Tonghma Habakkuk he ram a hinghong \it (chaos)\it* tue vaengah kho a sak. Ram tlung Assyria neh Babylon kah tanah laklo kah Judah tah halangnah neh huencannah khaw muep yet. Tiktamnah mueh kawng dongah Job bangla Habakkuk loh Pathen te phaeng a tueng sak. Judah ah halangnah a om pawt hamla Boeipa taengah a bih. Judah dantat hamla Pathen loh Babylon a tueih pah. Habakkuk tah let coeng Babylon hlangtholh loh me tlamlae a a then aih a ti. Babylon kah a thae te Pathen loh a ueh tloel coeng dongah dan a tat. Pathen kongaih a vai pawt dongah Judah te ana mawn laeh saeh a ti. Pathen loh pilnam a khang vetih thaomnah a paek pawn ni.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
\io1 I. Tonghma kah kohuetnah rhaepnit \ior 1. 1—2. 20\ior*  
\io1 A. Kohuetnah a pacuek \ior 1. 1-11\ior*  
\io2 1. Israel kah tholhnah \ior 1. 2-4\ior*  
\io2 2. Pathen kah hlatnah \ior 1. 5-11\ior*  
\io1 B. Kohuetnah a pabae \ior 1. 12—2. 20\ior*  
\io2 1. Khalden kah a muennah \ior 1. 12—2. 1\ior*  
\io2 2. Israel kah daemnah \ior 2. 2-20\ior*  
\io1 II. Tonghma kah thangthuinah \ior 3. 1-19\ior*  
\io1 A. Ming tanglue \ior 3. 1\ior*  
\io1 B. Bihhoenah \ior 3. 2\ior*  
\io1 C. Pathen phoenah \ior 3. 3-15\ior*  
\io1 D. Tangnah aka cak \ior 3. 16-19\ior*  
\c 1  
\p
